    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start for the intro. To make it a bit more robust for the students, could you add a few specific historical examples or landmark Supreme Court cases where this concept was used to secure those civil rights? I want them to see the real-world impact.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
